<h1>
About the Ponderosa
</h1>
<article>
The Ponderosa Ranch is the 100,000 acre land owned by Ben Cartwright
and his three sons, Adam, Hoss(Eric), and Joseph(Little Joe).
The Ponderosa was approximatly east of Lake Tahoe and West of Washoe Lake,
Carson City, and Virginia City.
</article>
